descriptionHtml:
I liked the Ironman movies and the Avengers very much so I thought of doing a new Helmet.
I\'m not working on the full suit anymore, there is already a full suit from somebody else on steam. Anyways, if anybody is interested in finishing my work, I can send the 3dmesh per mail.

You can find it on the enchantmenttable in Dragonsreach in Whiterun
Vibranium Helmet
Heavy Armor
Weight 10
Value 1500
Armor Rating 45
